decks.notes: The deck revolves around quickly assembling a combo with Prossh, Skyraider of Kher to generate a large number of tokens and then sacrificing them for value. The deck includes various ways to ramp and generate mana quickly, as well as ways to tutor for key combo pieces such as Food Chain. The deck also includes disruption in the form of removal spells and hand disruption to protect the combo. The goal is to overwhelm the opponent with a massive army of tokens and deal lethal damage in one explosive turn. The deck is resilient and can win quickly if not disrupted by the opponent.

This deck focuses on fast, aggressive gameplay with a mix of creatures and spells to quickly overwhelm the opponent. Halana and Alena, Partners serve as versatile commanders to provide additional damage and flexibility to the deck. The deck includes a variety of creatures with powerful abilities like Carnage Tyrant and Ruric Thar, the Unbowed, as well as removal spells like Lightning Bolt and Abrade to deal with threats. It also includes ramp spells like Birds of Paradise and Utopia Sprawl to accelerate mana production and allow for explosive turns. The goal is to put pressure on the opponent early and maintain board control while utilizing the partner commanders' abilities to maximize damage output.
